name: gyrex-jaxrs-application
body:
### Welcome to the Gyrex Jersey JAX-RS AddOn
This is a p2 software site. It's intended to be used directly in a Target Platform or for installation purposes.

Please note, the project is in the process of moving to Eclipse.org. We are just waiting for final IP approval of the Jersey library. The main code already moved to http://git.eclipse.org/c/gyrex/addons/gyrex-jersey-jaxrs.git/.

### Support or Contact
Having trouble? Please ask on the forums at http://www.eclipse.org/forums or contact support@ageto.net for professional support.
